  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2027510/extras/b22ba217af220db997230ea7a16f7cf8.poster.avif?t=1773127140\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2027510/extras/b22ba217af220db997230ea7a16f7cf8.webm?t=1773127140\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2027510/extras/b22ba217af220db997230ea7a16f7cf8.mp4?t=1773127140\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2027510/extras/78967d9e3b97c2fa80c05653dcb084ee.webp?t=1773127140\" width=576 height=47 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Inspired by the classic Atari GAUNTLET arcade game!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Slaughter hordes of monsters in fast-paced arcade action</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Progress through multiple dungeon crawls with different challenges</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2027510/extras/4065a749e8efa3a4a28fab3c59c7f5c9.poster.avif?t=1773127140\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2027510/extras/4065a749e8efa3a4a28fab3c59c7f5c9.webm?t=1773127140\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2027510/extras/4065a749e8efa3a4a28fab3c59c7f5c9.mp4?t=1773127140\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2027510/extras/0225c4bf59d55ba14d34878cf8977eca.webp?t=1773127140\" width=576 height=47 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover Relic rooms, open the chests, and choose!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build around different effects and combinations</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Wide range of relics including pets, utilities, buffs and new attacks</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2027510/extras/a8badda9c653d8ad5a135f518637ea83.poster.avif?t=1773127140\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2027510/extras/a8badda9c653d8ad5a135f518637ea83.webm?t=1773127140\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2027510/extras/a8badda9c653d8ad5a135f518637ea83.mp4?t=1773127140\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2027510/extras/a141ab962d81e69d6a846fe0681f0e7f.webp?t=1773127140\" width=576 height=47 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore wide open areas, packed mazes, switches and portal madness</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tackle Challenge Rooms to win rewards</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Treasures, keys, doors, bombs, traps and secrets</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Battle a variety of monsters, each with different abilities and challenge levels</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2027510/extras/0cdf971bdd82ef28f20f925f8aa033ca.poster.avif?t=1773127140\" width=600 height=75 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2027510/extras/0cdf971bdd82ef28f20f925f8aa033ca.webm?t=1773127140\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2027510/extras/552c6524a874b6b6cf37d88250a7ac18.webp?t=1773127140\" width=576 height=47 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Progress though multiple Monster Bosses, from <strong>Rat King</strong> to <strong>Ultimate Death</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock Boss Relics with run-changing effects</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2027510/extras/45ebab6e8acd3e7eafedf22091668473.poster.avif?t=1773127140\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2027510/extras/45ebab6e8acd3e7eafedf22091668473.webm?t=1773127140\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2027510/extras/45ebab6e8acd3e7eafedf22091668473.mp4?t=1773127140\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2027510/extras/d7121628fa9cbcc5e9495509c515b1ae.webp?t=1773127140\" width=576 height=47 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock multiple heroes with different unique attacks</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect gems to level up your hero, add or modify attacks</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experiment with an endless combination of effects</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2027510/extras/e6e88af3384843adcfa64ffdf7270bed.poster.avif?t=1773127140\" width=600 height=74 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2027510/extras/e6e88af3384843adcfa64ffdf7270bed.webm?t=1773127140\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2027510/extras/e6e88af3384843adcfa64ffdf7270bed.mp4?t=1773127140\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2027510/extras/735efeb996f5c1e61d076153f72f2b6a.webp?t=1773127140\" width=576 height=47 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Spend gold between runs to unlock new gameplay options</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Increase the power of Relics found within the dungeons</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2027510/extras/7365fedcc6490de183e38dcccc5c2069.webp?t=1773127140\" width=576 height=47 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Team up to crush your enemies with local co-op</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Steam Remote Play compatible</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Requires controller for second player</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2027510/extras/0954bec164e9fe4b39fe7b8cf55f8748.avif?t=1773127140\" width=600 height=236 /></span></p>",
